UI Branding plugin for GLPI
-------------------------------------------------------------------------

This plugin is distributed under the GNU General Public License v3.0

Original Inspiration: GLPI Modifications by i-Vertix/PGUM
Original Repository: https://github.com/i-Vertix/glpi-modifications

This version has been extensively modified and enhanced with:
- Interactive panel with notifications, events, and countdown
- Modern split-screen layouts
- Responsive design
- Custom escape system for multi-line content
- Native date picker integration
- Smooth animations and transitions
- Auto-scrolling for long lists
- Complete Twig integration

